://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijgDx1HoTPF0/v3/-1x-1.jpg" alt="President Trump, center left, met with oil executives in the East Room of the White House, following the ousting of Venezuela’s Nicolas Maduro, on Jan. 9." width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="1 月 9 日，委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗 (Nicolas Maduro) 下台后，特朗普总统（中左）在白宫东厅会见了石油业高管。" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijgDx1HoTPF0/v3/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt; 1 月 9 日，特朗普总统与石油高管会面。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Jim Lo Scalzo/EPA&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;几十年来&lt;/strong&gt;，世界上最大的大宗商品交易商一直试图置身于政治之外，进行自然资源买卖交易。现在，特朗普正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/k1e4o3y_u7GQbHkWZsRLoSJfJUQ9_4u9iyWOQ8tbTt2rMDwjlUfwiWU9FLrIpkoUGamzLoDTzQvD28j4vH6PuamMtBEE_rQ8jrp4n2Gct6uhl6YBJnKiDSOVz3DoekZ8xKpC7KaotYW1Spilfu5RXoBm31NmDZO89TkhCfP2AVnBPQYP4WYRH__Mcj9D3ntLqmGA14DMlbhdgPXyH3RIYvGnL4Djoar2vmJxdLNdptc7kFdTYb3vFspZ7qz-UWrdHBGJ8SI6DWHUQgygPaw_RUESIPYq3Bogk7-gxl7YMSjVN43t3qZSgMLu6zxM2wISeBOCi1mphJ1uRdqLvtWTlk56f4uS6Jmfzk-hm_js1bnPGaRJqtJyQSm-hmA1Fd3UMLX6xO-0sh3OfFo_b6CgEB8QgvU5NEg58jgMGaIeJm1NC4vN8NIUtu1S1OKWt_WHEWTdAiqBa7pzWwMheymqK2DPTrcfAY2bsrcb-k21aw8_nov4znhb81RkReNaI8EcwwzQy8K41Iqw331y-AzZpaDaOJ0PjRYt/6Sq9ThqrHAZmSMNQ9Egz3_gLuaJYYUu1/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="长期回避政治后，大宗商品交易员开始向特朗普示好"&gt;改变游戏规则&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;近几个月来，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国政府&lt;/strong&gt;更深入地进行大宗商品交易，授予合同或合作伙伴关系，这些合同或合作伙伴关系可能对参与者来说利润丰厚。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;当特朗普在取代委内瑞拉总统的军事行动后需要&lt;/strong&gt;迅速从委内瑞拉运出石油时，他呼吁维多和托克提供帮助，为他们提供可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Y6kQ6oXtgTwg4kF301qGyC3cw3Snwf0QlB5_vjNogLqWaMMch-sUIPbu2-Wo_jKh3a4HsUPTC5lnPdM4RNsGn2TXiO2tGNwPpnqqNe0bogMm4s_9dLlpgCUF4TTeJdpHgNVCWVFfygqzKdL7F1vgS7zDAOFP0cd2KE8kmt385OYu4IlEIo5HGS-ualKc6SBb0jX1aiFTq0peMbQQoYwMXK8ebwfqcexuyxnzz-hF3BTGiVcUcpjk5s4LCHMm0EEZ-K0T35fushio_7sUQz-rx0SSo8vze3MsOx1fFJc2PHLj21E3DPnuq2i5Fcqd_4LKcrJJL2DtKtEPme7fdxcm2-UcW-o8axZxnbfjkTY9qeeFdqDiTegAbW1NfE3QJuDtGzK5kLSJZPLe-ahxB95VLgVnI3lkLTsc2bH07m6Zw4G6guEzNeurwTsXmScNmhdF4QRsNg3bTU2FI_1-9CHWDwqkzAafaOZK2hFKbib_YAzQvyy6spFQWiwVnqKl5jLFYK0ACb9SRtbl8r6J2swjjw2VM0mPDlRWpMq3NWB5jw/HybfKBuMO-hFmGJpaLsbtnGAl97Rywdj/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="维多和托克：特朗普抢夺委内瑞拉石油的核心交易商"&gt;利润丰厚的特殊许可证&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;政治上的接近也在金属领域得到了回报&lt;/strong&gt;。摩科瑞的一家合资企业已开始将刚果民主共和国一座矿山的铜运往美国，这标志着刚果铜&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/WnU_I7J1xoGCWMhEtxfz5OrLlpcl4sgLtNsr-4f1pSJvgPtwpaSgnFKVyiG5kWqaMWFYCelLk5dDZD51Bi7zbwz9DKG_GffD0E76LndJlCJeVgH-NOVw-qyQpYuga8T5kTyhsXLByIZLmMcuswI4GSo9yY4b2b6m2QyMuS_M-M21CMobuOml6flWwDS85UxbOKVt5cPvVWBH-oR-rCVEV0p1GGMGN6eOi0kC2Cw--3vCEel01gPRsymDzZuaPLJS9oiK4r8q-HjC_F_o8WxfudngpIOaymGw_ZksM9YynQnCmXr6DTm9DUWtWkjzEGZRN8GPyCCR1I1gUSLfmHx9kaKjG49WtzC3wTtdK7LJAJcxQcjhME3drUAYG3u_SKNgz9IomUWDYuVVJlnnygBDl2ROD1_n90KnoOB3CEQQZbhvBgtN3HReWiLuL-KJ3BSB6yarB-qnQPmSd4NL4MWsoBnJZtqecgdlcQik9EZNpfXUDl-EwoT2bVsOuV2B_d2vdyRQDNxcM8kMumYYNfc0nHcQQv2D1i8/hMOVSiD8RZBAUrc1uQmL-JM6O9Bczd1J/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="摩科瑞投资的